    dc:description "Fig. 8. Pleuroseta ingens sp. nov. paratype (debu00160984).A. Male S6+7 and ring sclerite, ventrolateral view. B. Male surstylus, anterolateral view. Abbreviations: rs= ring sclerite. Scale bar: A=0.50 mm; B=0.30 mm." ;
